application_details.scheme_name: Your New Town Hall - Hambrook House

description: Redevelopment of site, including: - Demolition of Hambrook House to be replaced by a part 14, part 10 and part 4-6 storey mixed use building to provide residential with ground floor commercial (Class A1 and/or A3 use); - Demolition of No's 1-7 Town Hall Parade to be replaced by a 6-storey building to provide Office accomodation (Class B1 use); - Change of use and refurbishment of Ivor House to provide mixed use of residential together with basement and ground floor commercial (Class A1 and/or A3 use); - Change of use of the Press Building to provide a cycle hub and cafe (Class A1 and/or A3 use); and - Public realm improvements.
secondary_street_name: South Of Acre Lane; East Of Porden Road
